		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hi, <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />  I'm creating a game for the NES, and production isn't going that bad. I need to know how to make an engine though, so that the game actually works for testing and all that. The problem is, though, I know absolutely no programming. I really want to know it, but I never know where to start. What type of programming do I need to know, what specific functions mean for thatt programming, those are the questions I need to know.

		

		</td>
