	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Start with nerdy nights on Nintendoage. It'll basically explain everything. You can always ask questions once you start here. But there's lots to learn. 6502, good programming techniques, PPU, APU, CPU, etc.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


