	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I would suggest you should be pretty comfortable with chapter 1) and 2) from <a href="http://www.westerndesigncenter.com/wdc/documentation/Programmanual.pdf" class="postlink">here.</a> The rest of that document is pretty good too, but you could skip anything specific to 16-bit (65816) or 65c02, 65802.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


